These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, fanta
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, baseball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk | fanta   |
| Sport      | weightlifting    | baseball  | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, coffee
There are 3 different nationalities: french, russian, british
1. the french is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the russian is on the far left##1
3. the russian is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite | mirinda     | coffee      |
| Nationality   | russian | french | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: onion, eggplant, lemon
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea  | mirinda       |
| Food       | onion     | eggplant | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, papaya, garlic
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, gardening, video-games
1. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | garlic    | papaya     | kale |
| Hobby   | video-games | camping | gardening     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, scooter
1. the person driving the boat is the owner of the pony##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | rabbit | dog     | pony |
| Transport   | scooter        | skateboard | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, zucchini, broccoli
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile, helicopter
1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person eating broccoli is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | broccoli | asparagus      | zucchini  |
| Transport   | trike       | snowmobile | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, punk, electronic
3 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, frog
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of punk is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | ambient     | punk    |
| Pet           | horse | frog | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
