2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person eating apple is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | zucchini | kale | apple      |
| Hobby   | woodworking     | reading | gardening |

