3 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, frog
1. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
