.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, fanta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | water   | almond-milk    | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | fantasy | martial-arts |

