.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, metal, salsa
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, russian, colombian
1. the fan of salsa is the nigerian##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the colombian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | salsa   | metal  |
| Nationality   | colombian    | nigerian | russian |

