.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, jazz
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, japanese, italian
1. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | blues     | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | japanese | argentine | italian |

