.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, papaya, cabbage
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, firefighter, writer
1. the firefighter is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
2. the person eating cabbage is in the middle##1
3. the teacher is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | carrot     | cabbage   | papaya     |
| Job    | writer | firefighter | teacher |

