3 different pets are kept: goat, dog, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the police-officer is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | firefighter    | police-officer | nurse |
| Pet   | horse | goat     | dog        |

