.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, dubstep, r&b
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | water  | coffee | hot-chocolate  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | r&b   | house |

