.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, asparagus, radish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | radish | raspberry       | asparagus  |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | biathlon | badminton |

 